screen_desc: The screenshot displays the YouTube app interface on a mobile device. At the top, there is a search bar labeled "Search YouTube." The list continues with other entries such as "thuancapital," "eminem freestyle," "doraemon," "skyler," and "miyavi." The overall theme is dark, typical of the YouTube app design.
